<http://www.spektrix.com/gatewaytheatre/event/96601ALSQGSDJLRHKNNNJQDSSMHMHMNJQ> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Musical Theatre Performance";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Musical Theatre Performance</span><span><br/></span>Ages 11-18<span><br/></span>Sept 14, 2026 - Apr 24, 2027<span><br/></span>Mondays, 5:00pm-8:00pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Musical Theatre Performance is an auditioned class that balances our process-focused approach with an added goal of public performance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The first half of the year is dedicated to ensemble and skill-building, as students are introduced to the presentation material; the second half of the year focuses on rehearsal towards the students’ year-end presentation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To provide a more robust performance experience, production elements such as costumes, props and lights will be included in the year-end presentation. The class will have a tech rehearsal with these production elements. Up to three public performances will showcase the presentation in April 2027.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Mandatory class dates:<span><br/></span>Mon., March 8, April 5, 12, & 16, 2027 – Rehearsals<span><br/></span>Mon., April 19, 2027 – Final Run<span><br/></span>Wed., April 21, 2027 – Tech<span><br/></span>Thurs., April 22, 2027 – Show 1 (6pm)<span><br/></span>Fri., April 23, 2027 – Show 2 (10am) & Show 3 (1:30pm)<span><br/></span>Sat., April 24, 2027 – Show 4 (6pm)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Registration for this class is by audition only. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please note: All class withdrawals are subject to a 30% course withdrawal fee. View full <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.gatewaytheatre.com/gateway-academy-terms-conditions\">Refund/Cancellation Policy here</a>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-09-14T17:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
